    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Make Property Secure by Proper Will</strong>&mdash;Those who are faithful stewards of the Lord&apos;s means will know just how their business stands, and, like wise men, they will be prepared for any emergency. Should their probation close suddenly, they would not leave such great perplexity upon those who are called to settle their estate.",
