    "refcode_short": "AH 396.5",
    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 396.5 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Many are not exercised upon the subject of making their wills while they are in apparent health. But this precaution should be taken by our brethren. They should know their financial standing and should not <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"397\"></span> allow their business to become entangled. They should arrange their property in such a manner that they may leave it at any time.",
    "puborder": 1234,
    "translations": [
